title: Aishwarya's Comeback 'Jazbaa' Grosses 15.24 Crores in Opening Weekend
text:
Email 0 
NEW DELHI: Aishwarya Rai Bachchan’s comeback movie ‘Jazbaa’ bagged Rs 15.24 crores in its opening weekend. 
Revealing the box office figure of the flic,k trade analyst Taran Adarsh tweeted, “#Jazbaa maintained a STRONG hold on Sun. Fri 4.23 cr, Sat 5.49 cr, Sun 5.52 cr. Total: 15.24 cr. India biz.” 
Directed by Sanjay Gupta the film is an action thriller that also stars Irrfan Khan in the role of a police cop.
